data.description: LOVELY 2 BEDROOM 2 BATHROOM SINGLE FAMILY HOME IN THE ALL AGES WESTWOOD COMMUNITY IN TAMARAC. ENJOY WELCOMING CURB APPEAL COMPLETE WITH WELL-MANICURED LANDSCAPING AND A FRONT PORTION PERFECT FOR ENJOYING THE EVENING BREEZE. INTERIOR IS FILLED WITH NATURAL LIGHT, HAS TILE FLOORS THROUGHOUT, AND FEATURES SPACIOUS LIVING AREAS. DESIRABLE SPLIT FOR PLAN FOR PRIVACY WITH AN ELEGANT PRIMARY SUITE OFFERS UPDATED PLANK FLOORING AND ENSUITE BATH COMPLETE WITH DOUBLE VANITY. LARGE FLORIDA ROOM CAN BE USED AN AS OFFICE OR FLEX SPACE. THE OVERSIZED YARD FULLY FENCED YARD HAS A LARGE BACK PORCH AND PLENTY OF ROOM FOR A POOL ON ON 8,302 SF FT PREMIUM LOT. OTHER FEATURES INCLUDE A DEDICATED LAUNDRY AREA AND ONE CAR GARAGE. ALL IN A WELL-MAINTAINED COMMUNITY WITH LOW HOA FEES, NO BUYER APPROVAL REQUIRED.
